WEBVTT

00:00.140 --> 00:03.090
Previously on Transformers Prime

00:03.630 --> 00:07.070
It's as if the blood of
Unicron the Destroyer

00:07.740 --> 00:09.930
flows through my veins!

00:11.190 --> 00:12.970
Dark Energon?

00:13.000 --> 00:16.260
It's so scarce seems to
be virtually non-existent.

00:16.300 --> 00:18.180
Contact with civilians!

00:18.970 --> 00:20.590
We are protecting them.

00:21.280 --> 00:23.330
Fetch me this 'Fowler'.

00:24.070 --> 00:27.320
Tell me the location
of the Autobot base.

00:27.360 --> 00:28.860
It's an S.O.S.

00:35.320 --> 00:36.820
Scrap!

00:37.020 --> 00:39.810
Rise, my army!

00:39.840 --> 00:45.610
Behold the power
of Dark Energon!

