01:01.200 --> 01:04.010
Megatron has desecrated
the resting place

01:04.010 --> 01:05.890
of our fallen ancestors.

01:05.920 --> 01:07.580
And his own.

01:07.610 --> 01:11.270
Not even the dead
are free from his warmongering.

01:13.970 --> 01:16.720
At last, symbiosis.

01:17.070 --> 01:21.470
I can feel it. I possess complete
control over my army.

01:22.260 --> 01:24.210
Destroy them!

01:38.940 --> 01:42.040
Optimus, if our combatants
are already deceased,

01:42.080 --> 01:44.600
how can we possibly defeat them?

